data.description: Welcome home to this cute 3 bedroom 2 full bath home in the Linden School district! Beautiful fully fenced in back yard with extra one car garage/barn in backyard with loft area. Two wood fireplaces in home. Beautiful wood flooring throughout. Attached 2 car garage with extra space for storage or work bench area. Bonus room could be used as a fourth bedroom - right off garage and next to second bathroom. Large back four seasons room. Whole house generex system.  Home is being sold "as is". There is some needed TLC to make this home perfect.  Front facia is needing work and front porch needs some remodeling. Price is set accordingly.  Come take a look today! This is a great opportunity to live in a beautiful home in a great school district. Great location! Close to lakes, parks, shopping and highways. This would be a great home for a family or single living! Sale subject to probate court approval. Please call Amanda for details.
